ultra-for-higher-end-chips-130100277.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/intel-drops-i-processor-branding-after-15-years-introduces-ultra-for-higher-end-chips-130100277.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 58ebeb3b-c044-4a27-a3ff-87f5a3d3a6b1</guid><dc:creator>曹彼得</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Thu, 15 Jun 2023 13:00:00 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686769835</ingested><modified> 2023-06-14T19:10:43+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Computing]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Peter Cao]]></category><media:content height="759" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/714c04e0-0ae5-11ee-baff-ff7282cb0152" width="1316"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="759" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/714c04e0-0ae5-11ee-baff-ff7282cb0152" width="1316"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Intel]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Intel Core Ultra 3/5/7/9 family]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Intel Ultra Chip family]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Everything you need to know about Amazon Prime Day 2023]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> This year&#39;s <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9wcmltZWRheT90YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby0xMzYtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImFhZGQwNTk2LTE2MGItNGVlMi1iMjA0LTgxMzZhYWI5Y2U2MyJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAX837ZTQn2WaUZMGViHZ2kjocC3Tu6-lp0fgM_hpyNGD&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fprimeday" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/primeday?" class="rapid-with-clickid">Amazon Prime Day</a> is likely right around the corner, so it&#39;s a good time to start thinking about the things you&#39;ll want to look for once the deal wave hits. Everything from gadgets to clothes to household necessities will be on sale during the event, and if you&#39;re a Prime member, you&#39;ll have access to all of the deals on Amazon&#39;s site. Engadget will be surfacing all of the best tech deals we can find – both on Amazon and elsewhere – but there are some important things to know ahead of time so you can get exactly what you want out of this year&#39;s Prime Day.</p><h2> When is Amazon Prime Day?</h2><p> It&#39;s still unclear when Amazon Prime Day 2023 will take place. If Amazon follows the familiar pattern, Prime Day 2023 could be mid-July: the two-day sale event took place on July 12th and 13th in 2022. Since it&#39;s already the middle of June, we expect Amazon to publicly announce the dates for Prime Day 2023 soon and we&#39;ll update this post once that information becomes available.</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><h2> What is Amazon Prime Day?</h2><p> Amazon&#39;s annual shopping event surfaces exclusive deals for Prime members, which means you&#39;ll have to be a Prime subscriber on Prime Day to take advantage of any of the savings. Amazon still offers a <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9hbWF6b25wcmltZT90YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby0xMzYtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImFhZGQwNTk2LTE2MGItNGVlMi1iMjA0LTgxMzZhYWI5Y2U2MyJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAZ9en9ILuaNwxm92Kt0Q6fQuT38iLpE4b8e0pWzNo6xO&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Famazonprime" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/amazonprime?" class="rapid-with-clickid">30-day free trial</a> to new Prime subscribers, so you can start your free trial now and participate in the event.</p><p> If you don&#39;t pay for Prime and have no intention of doing so, you should still check out Amazon on Prime Day for sales that are available to all shoppers. Plus, other retailers like <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Walmart;elmt:;cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=3719d8d4-5edd-4817-998a-91f3229e7323&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Walmart&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiIzNzE5ZDhkNC01ZWRkLTQ4MTctOTk4YS05MWYzMjI5ZTczMjMiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud2FsbWFydC5jb20vPyIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiYWFkZDA1OTYtMTYwYi00ZWUyLWIyMDQtODEzNmFhYjljZTYzIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAX2XptCwYEW6ti19z1K_XsTJTPVBSWEktH83dKSVZ3Ab&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2F%3F" class="rapid-with-clickid">Walmart</a> , <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Best Buy;elmt:;cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=5e0bed65-d2f8-4b34-9b8f-955218c0e37a&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Best+Buy&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI1ZTBiZWQ2NS1kMmY4LTRiMzQtOWI4Zi05NTUyMThjMGUzN2EiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmVzdGJ1eS5jb20vPyIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiYWFkZDA1OTYtMTYwYi00ZWUyLWIyMDQtODEzNmFhYjljZTYzIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAXKsAV28C9InnmipgZsNMaIbZSuNFiP4r7c5gCMcCgMi&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bestbuy.com%2F%3F" class="rapid-with-clickid">Best Buy</a> and <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Target;elmt:;cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=827d7835-78d6-4491-ae04-c042cab1d6e7&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Target&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI4MjdkNzgzNS03OGQ2LTQ0OTEtYWUwNC1jMDQyY2FiMWQ2ZTciLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudGFyZ2V0LmNvbS8_IiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJhYWRkMDU5Ni0xNjBiLTRlZTItYjIwNC04MTM2YWFiOWNlNjMifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAQymQZxgQqbAP8ul3LHv9uFZ4rHzmN0nDih87Z9ZMaEK&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.target.com%2F%3F" class="rapid-with-clickid">Target</a> will have their own competing Prime Day sales during that time frame, too.</p><h2> Amazon Prime Day deals</h2><p> There may be official dates for Amazon Prime Day, but for the past few years, the company has started pushing out deals well before the event actually kicks off. We expect to see Amazon Prime Day early access deals this year, too.</p><p> Be they early Prime Day deals or day-of sales, <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAASppi1eDoKGc3ZAvEIm0eMVU-bE0IXbDWmW9BKEHloum&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fb%3Fie%3D%26node%3D2102313011" class="rapid-with-clickid">Amazon gadgets</a> are almost guaranteed to be discounted for the event. You can safely bet on things like Echo speakers, Kindle e-readers and Fire TV devices to be at record-low prices for Prime Day, so if you&#39;ve had your eye on one of those items, Prime Day is the time to buy. Prime Day is only matched by Black Friday in its discounts, so while that means you will likely have another chance to get that smart speaker for dirt cheap, it probably won&#39;t be until the holiday shopping season.</p><p> Make no mistake, Amazon gadgets will not be the only items discounted on Prime Day. You&#39;ll find clothes, shoes, household items, appliances, accessories and more on sale, but here at Engadget, we&#39;ll naturally be focusing on electronics. We expect this year&#39;s Prime Day to be like last year&#39;s, in that it will bring big discounts on headphones, earbuds, gaming accessories, SSDs and microSD cards, robot vacuums and more. </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-09/c4f5b210-edf8-11ea-bfdf-78df2c9073b2" style="" alt="Indianapolis - Circa July 2019: Amazon Prime delivery van. Amazon.com is getting In the delivery business With Prime branded vans" data-uuid="eef1f8fa-a79e-3ddb-b2a0-e74ceb7ce7c4"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> jetcityimage via Getty Images</div></figure><p> It&#39;s also worth mentioning the types of deals you can expect to see on Prime Day. Some deals will be live for the entire event, while others will be one-day-only sales. Those are the hardest to predict, since Amazon usually does not give any indication how long a given sale will last. Our recommendation is to buy the things you&#39;re most keen on as soon as you see them drop in price – that will ensure you get it while the discount is available, and while the item is still in stock.</p><p> You can also expect to see some “Lightning deals” happen during Prime Day. Thankfully, these are usually clearly labeled with the amount of time remaining to grab the deal noted on the product page. In our experience, only a handful of these flash sales are actually worth your money, but if you see something that&#39;s been on your wishlist drop in price for the next few hours, it&#39;s in your best interest to grab it immediately.</p><h2> How to prep for Amazon Prime Day</h2><p> We&#39;ve alluded to this already, but it&#39;s best to go into Amazon Prime Day as prepared as possible. That essentially means knowing exactly what you want to look for so you stay focused and avoid distractions. The whole of Amazon.com will be overwhelming on Prime Day, so the less time you spend aimlessly browsing, the more your wallet will thank you later.</p><p> Two simple things you can do ahead of Prime Day are make a list and bookmark a price tracker. For the former, take note of the most important items you want to pick up on Prime Day. You can either do this the old-fashioned way on a sticky note, or you can use Amazon&#39;s wish list feature. For the latter, add the items you want to buy on Prime Day to your wish list (or, even better, make a dedicated wishlist with only your Prime Day desirables) and return to that list during the shopping event. Not only will you have everything you want all in one place, but you&#39;ll also be able to see which of those items are cheaper on Prime Day than they were when you originally added them to your list.</p><p> As for the price tracker, sites like <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://camelcamelcamel.com/">CamelCamelCamel</a> let you monitor the price of specific items on Amazon. You can check out price history charts and you can make your own price-drop alerts, receiving emails when something you want gets a discount. CamelCamelCamel also has some browser extensions you can download so you don&#39;t have to navigate away from an Amazon product page to check its price history.</p><p> We know that not everyone – not even every Prime member – will be flocking to Amazon during Prime Day. Whether you find such blatant displays of consumerism off putting or you simply don&#39;t want to give Amazon more of your money, there are plenty of reasons why you might be skipping Prime Day all together. But that doesn&#39;t mean you have to skip <em>all</em> of the sales that will be happening during that same time. Retailers like Walmart, Target, Best Buy and others will all have competing Prime Day sales and many of them will match the discounted prices you&#39;ll find on Amazon. We recommend checking them out if you want to pick up a couple of things for less without spending money on Amazon.</p><p> Engadget will be covering the entirety of Prime Day, so if you have a lot of tech on your to-buy list, be sure to check back here on Prime Day for the best tech sales we could find. We&#39;ll be sure to include gadgets from across the board – from headphones to robot vacuums to gaming gear – plus the best “anti-Prime Day” deals you can find from other retailers. You can also follow the <a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/EngadgetDeals">@EngadgetDeals Twitter account</a> and subscribe to the <a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://subscription.yahoo.net/Newsletter/Preference/sub?b=engadgetdeals&amp;src">Engadget Deals newsletter</a> to stay up to date on the latest discounts. The volume of deals will be daunting, but we sift through them all and pick out the best ones to make Prime Day a bit easier for you.</p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/amazon-prime-day-2023-124519231.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/amazon-prime-day-2023-124519231.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> aadd0596-160b-4ee2-b204-8136aab9ce63</guid><dc:creator>瓦伦蒂娜·帕拉迪诺</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Thu, 15 Jun 2023 12:45:19 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686833120</ingested><modified> 2023-06-15T12:45:37+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Shopping]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Valentina Palladino]]></category><media:content height="1080" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/e5ce4ba0-0ad8-11ee-affe-11bc09e9224c" width="1920"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1080" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/e5ce4ba0-0ad8-11ee-affe-11bc09e9224c" width="1920"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Amazon Prime Day]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Amazon Prime Day]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[MSI Stealth 14 Studio review: A redesign done right]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> MSI 的 Stealth 笔记本电脑长期以来一直是我最喜欢的游戏笔记本电脑系列之一，这要归功于它们兼具性能和便携性。但<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/msi-stealth-15m-review-coasting-on-its-good-looks-192429083.html">去年的模型</a>令人失望。在坚持相同的设计几年后，它的底盘感觉很累，更新的规格也没有解决系统的根本问题。但对于 2023 年，MSI 对 Stealth 进行了全面改造，包括全新设计、可选的 240Hz 显示屏、更强大的组件以及两种尺寸可供选择。哎呀，添加的东西太多了微星甚至更改了整个系列的名称：The Stealth Studio。 After using one for the past few weeks, I feel like we might be looking at the most improved <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-gaming-laptops-172033838.html">gaming laptop</a> of the year.</p><h2>设计</h2><p>我一直在测试 14 英寸版本，但还有更大的 16 英寸型号，两种尺寸都采用光滑的镁铝外壳，有两种颜色可供选择：纯白色和星蓝色。不可否认，白色模型不是很隐蔽，但我不在乎，因为它看起来很棒<em>而且</em>超轻。它的重量仅为 3.75 磅，几乎比<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Dell;elmt:;cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=b1bb23c9-a2d4-4e4e-bfac-7a560ebe7641&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Dell&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAbwQrP1FNYqhaH048627QGKtoq5uvT24cnUdtoiE0DYH&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dell.com%2Fen-us%2Fshop%2Fdell-laptops%2Falienware-x14-r2-gaming-laptop%2Fspd%2Falienware-x14-r2-laptop" class="rapid-with-clickid">Alienware x14 R2</a>等竞争对手轻了整整半磅。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><div id="2a199b45b84c42dda5699cb76722bd6f"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/6lAnkgJ2uqQ?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen scrolling="no"></iframe></div><p><core-commerce id="86197979a2af46a4a03ab5799a0f8795" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>尽管它的尺寸很小，但您仍然可以获得可靠的连接，包括三个 USB 端口（一个 Type-A 和两个 Type-C）和一个全尺寸 HDMI 插孔。但更重要的是，整个系统中有大量微小的功能，显示出 MSI 对细节的关注。在后面的通风口上，格栅拼出了系统的名称，有点像你可能会坐上跑车。在前面，MSI 与 SteelSeries 合作，在其键盘上提供华丽的 RGB 照明。微星还在前面添加了一些小型的向上发声立体声扬声器，与之前的型号相比，音质有了很好的提升。您甚至可以获得网络摄像头的物理快门。当然，它只是一个小塑料盖，但我很高兴它在那里。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/48b2a5d0-0a21-11ee-8ff4-7db89f0b2102" style="height:1200px;width:2000px;" alt="Stealth 14 Studio 设计的巧妙之处之一是后方 RGB 照明，它拼出了系统的名称。" data-uuid="f383f85f-4129-3946-8cec-abb303579d8d"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> Sam Rutherford/Engadget 摄</div></figure><p>我的两个小抱怨是网络摄像头只有 720p——来吧 MSI，它是 2023——屏幕下方的下巴看起来有点笨拙。即使你忽略它有多大，我也希望 MSI 有一个铰链可以减少显示器和面板之间的间隙，因为在工作或玩游戏时看到尾灯闪耀会让人分心。</p><h2>展示</h2><p>默认情况下，Stealth 14 Studio 配备 1920 x 1200 165Hz IPS 显示屏，这是一个很好的起点。然而，我们的评测单元拥有 MSI 升级的 2560 x 1600 240Hz 屏幕，这真是一种享受。在测试中，我测得峰值亮度略低于 450 尼特，几乎是去年机器的两倍。这使得它非常适合玩各种游戏，而且由于色域覆盖了 100% 的 DCI-P3 光谱，它还可以作为照片或视频编辑工作站发挥双重作用。</p><h2>表现</h2><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/93a35ee0-0a21-11ee-abff-68b1230d2eac" style="height:1200px;width:2000px;" alt="与之前的型号类似，MSI 已与 SteelSeries 合作，提供一种在 Stealth 14 Studio 上自定义 RGB 背光的简便方法。" data-uuid="d4f24306-999e-3fd3-a82e-3a2800016523"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> Sam Rutherford/Engadget 摄</div></figure><p>Stealth 14 Studio 配备英特尔酷睿 i7-13700H 芯片、NVIDIA RTX 4060、16GB 内存和 1TB 固态硬盘，性能足以胜任几乎所有任务。在<em>Cyber​​punk 2077</em>和<em>Returnal</em>等游戏中，在 1080p 和最大设置下，Stealth Studio 分别达到了 67 和 78 fps，这实际上比我从具有相同 GPU 和 i9 芯片的 Razer Blade 18 上获得的要高一点。</p><p>当您考虑到 MSI 较小的机箱意味着它内部管理热量的空间更少时，这真是令人印象深刻。即使在像 PCMark 10 这样的综合测试中，Stealth Studio 也以 8,126 分对 7,236 分击败了 Blade 18，尽管 Razer 的价格比 MSI 高出 1,000 多美元。这只是表明更大更贵并不总是更好。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/6ed86ce0-0a21-11ee-9fff-5a1ba2bc4e71" style="height:1200px;width:2000px;" alt="Stealth 14 Studio 的另一个不错的生活质量调整是一个简单的内置网络摄像头快门。" data-uuid="cb1523f1-f9c9-3d45-9b68-31c835169488"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> Sam Rutherford/Engadget 摄</div></figure><p>最近，我玩了很多<em>暗黑破坏神 4</em> ，它真正展示了 Stealth 14 Studio 的功能。您可以调低图形以利用屏幕的快速刷新率，或者启用游戏的所有铃声和口哨声，同时仍保持远高于 60 fps。</p><p> Stealth 14 Studio 性能的两个小缺点是它运行起来有点热，而且它配备了 RTX 4070，考虑到它的尺寸，这是可以理解的。我试着一边看电视一边把它放在腿上玩，相信我，当我说它真的很烤的时候。因此，除非您有笔记本电脑，否则最好坐在办公桌前。</p><h2>电池寿命</h2><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/ce1f8360-0a2a-11ee-b5bd-7c76b7475ee6" style="height:1200px;width:2000px;" alt="除了系统右侧的一个 USB-C、一个 USB-A 和一个耳机插孔外，Stealth 14 Studio 还具有一个全尺寸 HDMI 插孔和另一个 USB-C 端口。" data-uuid="202126f0-2944-39a2-a402-afb7ac64a7b2"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> Sam Rutherford/Engadget 摄</div></figure><p>去年的模型在四个多小时后就崩溃了，MSI 在这里也取得了一些显着的进步。在我们的视频测试中，Stealth 14 Studio 持续了 5 小时 19 分钟，比去年的系统增加了 25%。但更棒的是，它还击败了更大的竞争对手（配备更大的电池），包括<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/razer-blade-16-review-4k-1080p-miniled-screen-151100229.html">Blade 16 (5:01)</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/asus-rog-zephyrus-m16-2023-review-big-performance-with-a-brilliant-display-134540091.html">华硕的 ROG Zephyrus M16 (4:38)</a> 。</p><h2>包起来</h2><p>Stealth 14 Studio 几乎是 MSI 轻薄游戏产品线的彻底转变。它采用引人注目的新设计、更新的内部结构和一些受欢迎的生活质量升级——所有这些都在一个易于携带的底盘中；我已经用它进行了多次越野旅行，它还没有让我失望。事实上，Stealth 14 Studio 基本上拥有我在一个伟大的多面手身上寻找的一切——好吧，除了 OLED 屏幕或 SD 卡插槽（尽管你在更大的 16 英寸型号上确实有一个）。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/05a84790-0a2b-11ee-bf7b-915f340c6b1e" style="height:1200px;width:2000px;" alt="综合考虑，Stealth 14 Studio 的热通风孔和不支持 RTX 4080 GPU 是相对较小的缺点。" data-uuid="0930fab4-d424-33de-8fb2-593c5a406005"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> Sam Rutherford/Engadget 摄</div></figure><p>但是，如果这些对您来说都不是交易破坏者，MSI 已经提供了一个系统，该系统为游戏或您可能需要的任何其他东西提供了惊人的构建和稳定的性能。 And with our upgraded model currently going for $1,900 (or around $1,700 for the base model), you&#39;re getting more storage and a faster CPU and GPU than a base Alienware x14 R2 for only $150 more.因此，在经历了低迷的一年之后，MSI 恢复了 Stealth——咳咳，Stealth Studio——恢复了昔日的辉煌，作为一个可以做所有事情同时看起来也很棒的系统。</p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/msi-stealth-14-studio-review-a-redesign-done-right-123028890.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/msi-stealth-14-studio-review-a-redesign-done-right-123028890.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 2b33f6e7-8f35-442e-9ac9-08190e272e23</guid><dc:creator> Sam Rutherford</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher> Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Thu, 15 Jun 2023 12:30:28 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686835050</ingested><modified> 2023-06-15T13:17:40+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Sam Rutherford]]></category><media:content height="1200" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/149ce850-0a21-11ee-abff-a4a97401f0c9" width="2000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1200" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/149ce850-0a21-11ee-abff-a4a97401f0c9" width="2000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Photo by Sam Rutherford/Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Thanks to a complete redesign for 2023, MSI's Stealth 14 Studio might be the most improved gaming laptop of the year.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[MSI Stealth 14 Studio gaming laptop]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[WhatsApp may soon let you add multiple accounts to one device]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>如果您经常使用经常使用多个 WhatsApp 帐户的人，您将会对这个新的测试版更新感兴趣。 <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://wabetainfo.com/whatsapp-beta-for-android-2-23-13-5-whats-new/"><em>据 WABetaInfo 报道，</em></a>据报道，该消息传递应用程序正在为其 Android 应用程序提供多帐户支持，这一更新将允许您在同一设备上的配置文件之间切换。该功能看起来就像在<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-02-05-instagram-account-linking.html">Meta 拥有的应用程序 Instagram</a>上更改帐户一样，应用程序底部的弹出窗口显示当前帐户和添加新帐户的选项。 </p><div id="84a0779282ed43698ad9d68baf9ae5cb"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">📝 适用于 Android 的 WhatsApp 测试版 2.23.13.5：有什么新功能？<br><br>感谢该应用程序的商业版本，我们发现 WhatsApp 正在开发多帐户功能，并将在该应用程序的未来更新中提供！ <a href="https://t.co/jDnLxnJtbv">https://t.co/jDnLxnJtbv</a> <a href="https://t.co/kz4PrYbCvX">pic.twitter.com/kz4PrYbCvX</a></p> - WABetaInfo (@WABetaInfo) <a href="https://twitter.com/WABetaInfo/status/1669119668492066824?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 6 月 14 日</a></blockquote></div><p>任何新帐户都将存储在您的设备中，当然，您可以随时注销。如果您有不同的工作号码和个人号码，或者想尝试最新的以社交媒体为中心的 WhatsApp 功能，例如<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/whatsapps-new-channels-feature-lets-accounts-send-one-way-updates-to-followers-090843232.html">Channels</a> ，那么多帐户支持可能是有利的。此更新可让您向关注者发送照片和民意调查等广播，WhatsApp 计划在未来为创作者将其货币化。同样，据报道，WhatsApp 一直在开发一种<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/whatsapp-may-soon-introduce-usernames-105558183.html">用户名功能</a>，可以让你像 Instagram 或 Twitter 一样找到人，而无需他们的电话号码。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>多帐户支持还遵循 iOS 和 Android 发布的伴侣模式，该更新允许您<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/whatsapp-now-lets-you-use-your-account-on-multiple-phones-163158921.html">在最多四部手机上使用同一个 WhatsApp 帐户</a>。以前，您只能在一台手机上登录，平板电脑和电脑也可以登录。</p><p>目前还没有关于何时可以从一台设备在帐户之间跳转的时间表。我们可以期待多帐户支持在完全发布后会得到广泛应用，但目前只能通过 Android 测试版更新看到。</p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/whatsapp-may-soon-let-you-add-multiple-accounts-to-one-device-121532162.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/whatsapp-may-soon-let-you-add-multiple-accounts-to-one-device-121532162.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 1f9f08d6-c322-4c6d-b25f-c6d864cd4599</guid><dc:creator>莎拉菲尔丁</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Thu, 15 Jun 2023 12:15:32 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686830319</ingested><modified> 2023-06-15T11:58:45+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Software]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Handheld & Connected Devices]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Sarah Fielding]]></category><media:co