用户对该工具的访问也将受到限制。他们可以通过<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://streamlabs.com/">Streamlabs 的免费版本</a>使用播客编辑器，每月免费编辑一小时的内容。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/341db310-0b68-11ee-bbfe-8188f215f07f" style="height:1156px;width:1920px;" alt="显示 Streamlabs 的新播客编辑器工具的屏幕截图。左侧是带有气泡的突出显示文本，上面写着" data-uuid="82223d30-8447-315a-9c27-132e09c6b5a5"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> Engadget</div></figure><p>罗技 G PC 游戏和创作者主管 Vincent Borel 表示：“Podcast Editor 现在使 Streamlabs 能够为创作者提供最强大的产品套件，无论他们身在何处都能接触到他们的观众，同时专注于他们最喜欢的内容创作元素- 流式传输并与他们的观众互动。”</p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/streamlabs-gets-an-ai-powered-podcast-editor-120041029.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/streamlabs-gets-an-ai-powered-podcast-editor-120041029.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 12cbd854-ade5-4e88-b6a5-8c0275807426</guid><dc:creator>玛丽拉月亮</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Thu, 15 Jun 2023 12:00:41 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686827150</ingested><modified> 2023-06-15T11:06:01+00:00</modified><category><![CDATA[Software]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Social & Online Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mariella Moon]]></category><media:content height="4480" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/08517240-0b62-11ee-9df7-92606429edc2" width="6720"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CD