rkforce-161529844.html">Sonos 裁员 7%</a></ins></p><p><ins> <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/ups-tentatively-agrees-to-add-air-conditioning-to-its-trucks-170010514.html">UPS 暂时同意为其卡车增加空调</a></ins></p><p><ins><a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-apple-watch-accessories-133025270.html">2023 年最佳 Apple Watch 配件</a></ins></p><p><ins><a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/amazons-echo-dot-comes-with-a-smart-plug-for-less-than-the-speaker-on-its-own-142920470.html">亚马逊的 Echo Dot 配备智能插头，价格低于扬声器本身</a></ins></p><p><ins><a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/mcdonalds-just-released-a-grimace-game-boy-color-game-093540230.html">麦当劳刚刚发布了一款 Grimace Game Boy Color 游戏</a></ins></p><p><ins><a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/armored-core-vi-fires-of-rubicon-first-look-140011240.html">“Armored Core VI Fires of Rubicon”第一眼：使用可定制机甲进行快速战斗</a></ins></p><p><ins><a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-wireless-mice-pc-gaming-mobile-150027822.html">我对完美生产力鼠标的追求</a></ins></p><p><ins><a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/microsoft-activision-blizzard-merger-temporarily-blocked-by-us-judge-061933491.html">美国法官暂时阻止微软与动视暴雪的合并</a></ins></p><h2><ins> <a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/ubisoft-needs-a-reboot-164531373.html">育碧需要重启</a></ins></h2><h3>曾经风靡一时的游戏巨头怎么了？</h3><p></p><p>我们的 Summer Game Fest 报道将目光转向了 Ubisoft，它是几个大型特许经营权的发源地，包括 Far Cry 和 Assassin&#39;s Creed。然而，在过去的几年里，该公司摇摆不定，发行了半生不熟、半受喜爱的游戏，结果却平平无奇。急转弯转向免费增值游戏，叹息，NFT 只会加速其好名声的侵蚀。想知道是什么幕后花絮导致了下滑吗？<ins> <a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/ubisoft-needs-a-reboot-164531373.html">我也是，直到我读到这篇文章</a></ins>.</p><p><ins> <a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/ubisoft-needs-a-reboot-164531373.html"><strong>继续阅读。</strong></a></ins></p><h2><ins> <a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/twitter-is-getting-evicted-from-its-colorado-office-over-unpaid-rent-185026284.html">推特因未付租金而被逐出科罗拉多办公室</a></ins></h2><h3>等等，拒绝付款会有后果！？</h3><p></p><p>法官有<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/twitter-is-getting-evicted-from-its-colorado-office-over-unpaid-rent-185026284.html">将推特从科罗拉多州的办公室中驱逐出去</a></ins>在大楼的所有者起诉要求拖欠三个月共计 75,000 美元的租金之后。该地点目前约有 150 名员工，他们必须在 7 月底之前收拾东西搬走。这也不会是 Twitter 律师唯一一次因所有者拒绝付款而进入法庭。它目前正被（深吸一口气）清洁工、旧金山房东和几名前雇员起诉，要求赔偿据称欠他们的款项。</p><p><ins> <a data-i13n="cpos:18;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/twitter-is-getting-evicted-from-its-colorado-office-over-unpaid-rent-185026284.html"><strong>继续阅读。</strong></a></ins></p><h2><ins> <a data-i13n="cpos:19;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/sennheiser-soundprotex-plus-review-concert-earplugs-that-dont-kill-the-vibe-193006468.html">Sennheiser SoundProtex Plus 评论：不会破坏氛围的音乐会耳塞</a></ins></h2><h3>在您摇滚时保护您的听力。</h3><figure> <a href="https://www.engadget.com/sennheiser-soundprotex-plus-review-concert-earplugs-that-dont-kill-the-vibe-193006468.html"><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/9c044490-0b62-11ee-bf87-6e23466a08fc" style="height:416px;width:625px;" alt="在后院的桌子上拍摄的 Sennheiser SoundProtex Plus 包装图片。" data-uuid="7cfb5755-c696-34d5-8859-d87aa19a5425"></a><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> <a href="https://www.engadget.com/sennheiser-soundprotex-plus-review-concert-earplugs-that-dont-kill-the-vibe-193006468.html">比利·斯蒂尔/Engadget 摄</a></div></figure><p>如果您是现场音乐的忠实粉丝，您可能已经被警告过所有这些大型 PA 系统可能对您的听力造成的伤害。 Sennheiser 的音频专家希望通过一对专为现场音乐活动设计的耳塞来解决这个问题。比利斯蒂尔已经<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:20;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/sennheiser-soundprotex-plus-review-concert-earplugs-that-dont-kill-the-vibe-193006468.html">测试 SoundProtex Plus</a></ins>通过花时间在嘈杂的演出中看看它们是否可以帮助您享受音乐而不影响您将来这样做的能力。</p><p><ins> <a data-i13n="cpos:21;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/sennheiser-soundprotex-plus-review-concert-earplugs-that-dont-kill-the-vibe-193006468.html"><strong>继续阅读。</strong></a></ins></p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><h2><ins> <a data-i13n="cpos:22;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-homes-new-script-editor-can-make-smart-device-automations-even-more-powerful-103019126.html">Google Home 的新脚本编辑器可以使智能设备自动化更加强大</a></ins></h2><h3>需要一些编程知识。</h3><figure> <a href="https://www.engadget.com/google-homes-new-script-editor-can-make-smart-device-automations-even-more-powerful-103019126.html"><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/ebbebab0-0b62-11ee-95fd-8fd5a3523f79" style="height:396px;width:625px;" alt="Google Home 新脚本设置的图片。" data-uuid="0adcba12-2a93-3acc-81d1-3ae264bbebf2"></a><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> <a href="https://www.engadget.com/google-homes-new-script-editor-can-make-smart-device-automations-even-more-powerful-103019126.html">谷歌</a></div></figure><p>谷歌重新设计的家庭应用是<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:23;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-homes-new-script-editor-can-make-smart-device-automations-even-more-powerful-103019126.html">介绍脚本编辑器</a></ins>，使用户能够编写自己的智能家居程序。这包括“如果这样”风格的指示，比如在天黑后客厅电视打开时调暗客厅灯光和放下百叶窗。它是为有一些编程经验的人设计的，但它应该足够简单，大多数忠实的业余爱好者至少应该尝试一下。</p><p><ins> <a data-i13n="cpos:24;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-homes-new-script-editor-can-make-smart-device-automations-even-more-powerful-103019126.html"><strong>继续阅读。</strong></a></ins></p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-anker-gets-into-the-home-solar-battery-game-111509903.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-anker-gets-into-the-home-solar-battery-game-111509903.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> ad0071ab-fab3-4be8-a1b4-d833e3dcf0e0</guid><dc:creator>丹尼尔·库珀</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Thu, 15 Jun 2023 11:15:09 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686823639</ingested><modified> 2023-06-15T10:07:24+0